        <div class="tut-back" onclick="goPage('knowledge')">← Back to Knowledge Hub</div>
        <div class="tut-tag">GeM Categories</div>
        <h1 class="tut-h1">Q1 to Q4 — Understanding<br>GeM Product Categories</h1>
        <p class="tut-hero-p">GeM classifies all products into four quadrants based on who can sell them. Knowing your product's category determines which suppliers can respond to your bid — and what quality to expect.</p>
        <div class="tut-meta">
          <span class="tut-pill">🔢 6 min read</span>
          <span class="tut-pill">🏛️ For Bid Officers</span>
          <span class="tut-pill">📦 Product Procurement</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="tut-body">
        <nav class="tut-toc">
          <div class="tut-toc-title">Contents</div>
          <a onclick="document.getElementById('tut-q-1').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',block:'start'})">What are Q Categories?</a>
